  "texts": [
    "Yet it is too difficult for LLMs to directly make decisions on challenging technical problems only by prompting.",
    "To balance efficiency and interpretability, one approach is to integrate the LLMs into certain search strategies, where the genetic algorithm guides the search process and LLMs generate the candidate crossovers.",
    "LLMatic [196] and EvoPrompting [197] use code-LLMs as mutation and crossover operators for a genetic NAS algorithm.",
    "During the evolution process, each generation has a certain probability of deciding whether to perform crossover or mutation to produce new offspring.",
    "Crossover and mutation are generated by prompting LLMs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "LLMatic [196] and EvoPrompting [197] use code-LLMs as mutation and crossover operators for a genetic NAS algorithm."
  ]
